@fulg<br /><br />Just to expand, if I were introducing some of your examples for the first time and I felt it was not obvious what the abbreviation or acronym is or that it might be mistaken for another meaning, I would mark them up as follows:<br /><br />&lt;dfn title=&quot;Short Message Service&quot;&gt;&lt;abbr&gt;SMS&lt;/abbr&gt;&lt;/dfn&gt;<br /><br />&lt;dfn title=&quot;Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome is the final stage of HIV disease&quot;&gt;&lt;acronym&gt;AIDS&lt;/acronym&gt;&lt;/dfn&gt;<br /><br />This once again highlights the need for &lt;acronym&gt;.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3652">Willabee</a> — Tue Oct 16, 2012 4:53 pm</p><hr />
